fy到㗎<br />\n「全世界都知佢哋成日亂嚟」，同「攻入中大係咪亂嚟」，係兩回事嚟㗎！<br />\n<br />\n一開始守中大，係因為班曱甴明顯冇理由入嚟，明顯係過分<br />\n但只限守，唔係攻，攻個目的係咩？方向係咩？<br />\n有班人前晚仲引戰，呢樣極離譜<br />\n<br />\n屌你，我中大㗎，中大我屋企嚟<br />\n我都好想守同守得住呀<br />\n但而家入面個情況係點，你知咩？<br />\n<br />\n鬧我五毛之前起我底，放我名上google<br />\n我想問返你，你喺唔喺中大？"},{"pid":"1c90f5a824618380d96f36e7e7caf68a49e63a0b","tid":1721561,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:19:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07018bd0126beab96974274429728d3e9fc52741","tid":1721561,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c99fc5dff51d5a74a0413bc28aeed6c57e4207","tid":1721561,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:09:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e722e72e22eebfa4393467f727063621daa2a4c","tid":1721561,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ee261e5d6a55956bffd21739c1dc3269759bee","tid":1721561,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f053ce58f815ea27d7729625015cc5507fceb20d","tid":1721561,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:19:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82fd47f796adb96d6d16b220f82841d63a715266","tid":1721561,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1cb7d7c750fddd3dbf0866f5ca420bf36d3f5d6","tid":1721561,"uid":198278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc